# Start Here

Before making any changes or answering questions about this codebase, read `PROJECT_MAP.md` in the project root.

It contains:
- What the app does and why
- Every file's purpose and the functions inside it
- Data flow from CSV load to export
- Known incomplete features
- How to run the project locally

Do not skip this step.

## Updating the Map
After any major change (new file, new struct, refactor, new convention),
update PROJECT_MAP.md before closing the task.
